
simple IPTV proxy, small, faster, compact

avail http/hls/udp/rtp input and output

for config used xml

can usage local or remote config
local config use from same dir
remote config setup from start param -ConfigUrl http://some url/some_config.xml

local config not update, only restart AvProxy reload config
remote config update from some time

if config changed all input and output will reconfigure
for update config just change (increase) ver number in xml Ver="1"

exmaple config

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="GB2312"?>
<AvProxy Ver="1">
<Entry Name="12" Url="http://frosite2.com:8080/url" />
<Entry Name="udp" Url="udp://231.1.1.1:1234?KeepAlive=61&amp;Source=192.168.60.129&amp;IFace=192.168.60.129" />
<Entry Name="98" Url="http://frosite3..any.com/url/any" />
<Entry Name="test" Url="http://frosite4.com" />
<Entry Name="any_name" Url="m3u8://frosite5.com/url/test.m3u8" />
</AvProxy>

where is input
http input use scheme http://
hls input use scheme m3u8://
rtp/udp input use as rtp:// or udp://

by default AvProxy bind to 80 port, but can be change -HttpPort 8080

output avail through http://ip/Apple/name of Entry
for exmaple
http://ip/Apple/12
http://ip/Apple/udp
http://ip/Apple/98
http://ip/Apple/test
http://ip/Apple/any_name

dobule entry name in confg will ignore

all input after start is active

for trace use -Trace option